description: AMUNDI MSCI EUROPE VALUE FACTOR UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the MSCI Europe Value strategy Index, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to easily follow around 300 leading value stocks in 15 European countries, with a single transaction. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi MSCI Europe Value Factor UCITS ETF - EUR (C)
